Subject: [RFC PATCH 05/30] linux/kernel.h: Add PTR_ALIGN_DOWN macro
Date:   Tue, 4 Jun 2019 18:44:51 +0530
Message-ID: <20190604131516.13596-6-kishon@ti.com>
X-Mailer: git-send-email 2.17.1
